cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DB, cs.CL, cs.CR

This paper deals with the integration of ontologies and nonmonotonic rules, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and logic (cs.LO). It also discusses knowledge updates, which is a common topic in databases (cs.DB) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper addresses the issue of closed world reasoning, which is a topic in cryptography and security (cs.CR).
